"tnoremap   <silent>   <F8>    <C-\><C-n>:FloatermPrev<CR>
"nnoremap   <silent>   <F9>    :FloatermNext<CR>
"tnoremap   <silent>   <F9>    <C-\><C-n>:FloatermNext<CR>
